The '''Tizo'pil Yun'tchilat''' or '''The Day of Comprehending the Will of the Gods''' was the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] ceremony where one [[dhuryam]] was chosen to be the [[World Brain]]. First, the thirteen dhuryams' telepathic contact with their slaves was disrupted by the [[Shreeyam'tiz]] in order to prevent last-minute sabotage. Then, the [[Shaper caste|shapers]] inspected the domains of each dhuryam in order to determine which was the most worthy. That dhuryam became the World Brain, assuming direct control over [[Coruscant/Legends|Yuuzhan'tar]] and managing the thousands of biological processes, and supervising the Vongforming and maintenance of Yuuzhan'tar. The remaining dhuryams were destroyed.

